  Q2 region-lifetime : use effect-row {Region<'r>} @ HIR ← confirmed
  Q3 AD-opt-in : [Differentiable] annotation @ HIR ← Slang-style confirmed
  Q4 generics : interfaces + associated-types @ HIR-level ← confirmed
  Q1 effect-discharge : HIR-level staged-check :
     ○ {NoAlloc} {NoRecurse} {DetRNG} {GPU}{CPU} = compile-time
     ○ {Deadline<N>} = compile-time-budget-tracking + runtime-assert
     Q1 ← resolved

