  Q5 stdlib-policy : bundled-and-vendored @ year-1 • pkg-mgr @ year-3
  Q7 hot-reload : preserve via .so-reload + effect-frozen-fingerprint
     ○ feel.toml pattern @ year-1

∎ Q6-DEEP-DIVE
  DECISION : LLVM-only year-1 • custom-MIR year-2 • MLIR-bridge optional year-3
